item.title: CVE-2019-0246|2024-08-04T17:44:16.331Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20cloud%20connector
item.description: SAP Cloud Connector, before version 2.11.3, does not perform any authentication checks for functionalities that require user identity.

item.title: CVE-2019-0247|2024-08-04T17:44:16.249Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20cloud%20connector
item.description: SAP Cloud Connector, before version 2.11.3, allows an attacker to inject code that can be executed by the application. An attacker could thereby control the behavior of the application.
